      <biogHist id="md5-6e8f13fd9832d64c09a58bb73ed7d0fa">
        <p>Drama teacher, 1944- .  A high school drama teacher for 15 years with the Calgary Catholic School Board, Ms. Potts received an MA in Education, specializing in drama education, from the University of Calgary.  The thesis for the MA degree generated the material for this collection.  She was a representative of Alberta Theatre Projects to the International Association of Theatre for Children and Young People Conference in Madrid, Spain, in 1978. She is a member of the Department of Education's Fine Arts Curriculum Coordinating Committee for the Province of Alberta.</p>
      </biogHist>
